description: An HTML website built on Quarto that documents the process and learnings of Grade Distribution Transformer and Class Schedule Scraper.
A Python script that processes all available PDF tables published by SMC. Extracts, cleans, and transforms grade distribution data into .csv and .RDATA files for easy access.
A Python script that scrapes all available class schedules published by SMC. Extracts, cleans, and transforms class schedule data into .csv and .RDATA files for easy access.
